                     <title type="lacunous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0086IHA">دلائل الخيرات</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar"/>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar"/>
                     <note>No printing information remains. The edition has further prayers printed in the margins. Some of the pages are loose and the order is disrupted. Missing pages have been replaced by handwritten copies. The lay-out of the handwritten pages is the same as on the printed pages.</note>
                     <note/>
